<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink305">
<l>kaḷiṟu piṭitaḻīip piṟapulam paṭarātu</l>
<l>pacitiṉa varuntum paitaṟu kuṉṟattuc</l>
<l>cuṭarttoṭik kuṟumaka ḷiṉaiya</l>
<l>veṉaippayañ ceyyumō viṭalainiṉ celavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O young man! Will your departure bring any benefit,</l>
<l>as the young girl with shining bangles laments in the mountains, 
devoid of green grass,</l>
<l>where male elephant is suffering, being eaten by hunger,</l>
<l>but still does not leave for other lands embracing [his] mate?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
